Class NumberRange

java.lang.Object
edu.monash.fit2099.engine.positions.NumberRange

public class NumberRange
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Integer>
A class that represents an array of sequential numbers. Counted for loops can cause off by one errors, and using this class can let you use enhanced for loops instead. Python programmers should be familiar with this idiom.
